{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891__seg-001", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-067", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891", "language": "en", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "老子 67.1", "sort_key": "067.001", "text_original": "All the world says that, while my Dao is great, it yet appears to be inferior (to other systems of teaching).", "text_normalized": "All the world says that, while my Dao is great, it yet appears to be inferior (to other systems of teaching).", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891__seg-002", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-067", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891", "language": "en", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "老子 67.2", "sort_key": "067.002", "text_original": "Now it is just its greatness that makes it seem to be inferior.", "text_normalized": "Now it is just its greatness that makes it seem to be inferior.", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891__seg-003", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-067", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891", "language": "en", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "老子 67.3", "sort_key": "067.003", "text_original": "If it were like any other (system), for long would its smallness have been known!", "text_normalized": "If it were like any other (system), for long would its smallness have been known!", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891__seg-004", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-067", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891", "language": "en", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "老子 67.4", "sort_key": "067.004", "text_original": "But I have three precious things which I prize and hold fast.", "text_normalized": "But I have three precious things which I prize and hold fast.", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891__seg-005", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-067", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891", "language": "en", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "老子 67.5", "sort_key": "067.005", "text_original": "The first is gentleness;", "text_normalized": "The first is gentleness;", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891__seg-006", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-067", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891", "language": "en", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "老子 67.6", "sort_key": "067.006", "text_original": "the second is economy;", "text_normalized": "the second is economy;", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891__seg-007", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-067", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891", "language": "en", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "老子 67.7", "sort_key": "067.007", "text_original": "and the third is shrinking from taking precedence of others.", "text_normalized": "and the third is shrinking from taking precedence of others.", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891__seg-008", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-067", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891", "language": "en", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "老子 67.8", "sort_key": "067.008", "text_original": "With that gentleness I can be bold;", "text_normalized": "With that gentleness I can be bold;", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891__seg-009", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-067", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891", "language": "en", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 9, "canonical_ref": "老子 67.9", "sort_key": "067.009", "text_original": "with that economy I can be liberal;", "text_normalized": "with that economy I can be liberal;", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891__seg-010", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-067", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891", "language": "en", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 10, "canonical_ref": "老子 67.10", "sort_key": "067.010", "text_original": "shrinking from taking precedence of others, I can become a vessel of the highest honour.", "text_normalized": "shrinking from taking precedence of others, I can become a vessel of the highest honour.", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891__seg-011", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-067", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891", "language": "en", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 11, "canonical_ref": "老子 67.11", "sort_key": "067.011", "text_original": "Now-a-days they give up gentleness and are all for being bold;", "text_normalized": "Now-a-days they give up gentleness and are all for being bold;", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891__seg-012", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-067", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891", "language": "en", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 12, "canonical_ref": "老子 67.12", "sort_key": "067.012", "text_original": "economy, and are all for being liberal;", "text_normalized": "economy, and are all for being liberal;", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891__seg-013", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-067", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891", "language": "en", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 13, "canonical_ref": "老子 67.13", "sort_key": "067.013", "text_original": "the hindmost place, and seek only to be foremost;", "text_normalized": "the hindmost place, and seek only to be foremost;", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891__seg-014", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-067", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891", "language": "en", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 14, "canonical_ref": "老子 67.14", "sort_key": "067.014", "text_original": "- (of all which the end is) death.", "text_normalized": "- (of all which the end is) death.", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891__seg-015", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-067", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891", "language": "en", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 15, "canonical_ref": "老子 67.15", "sort_key": "067.015", "text_original": "Gentleness is sure to be victorious even in battle, and firmly to maintain its ground.", "text_normalized": "Gentleness is sure to be victorious even in battle, and firmly to maintain its ground.", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891__seg-016", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-067", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-067__legge-chinesenotes-1891", "language": "en", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 16, "canonical_ref": "老子 67.16", "sort_key": "067.016", "text_original": "Heaven will save its possessor, by his (very) gentleness protecting him.", "text_normalized": "Heaven will save its possessor, by his (very) gentleness protecting him.", "notes": ""}
